  "rpgSnippet": "     P CreateClaim     B\n     D CreateClaim     PI\n     D*----------------------------------------------------------------\n     D create          S               N   Inz(*Off)\n     D maintenance     S               N   Inz(*Off)\n     D groups          S              4A   Inz(*Blanks)\n     D partNo          S              7A   Inz(*Blanks)\n     D partValue       S             11  2 Inz(0)\n     D text            S             65A   Dim(4) Inz(*Blanks)\n     D failureNo       S              2  0 Inz(0)\n     D lineNo          S              1  0 Inz(0)\n     D valueMat        S             11  2 Inz(0)\n     D valueLab        S             11  2 Inz(0)\n     D valueSpe        S             11  2 Inz(0)\n     D*****************************************************************\n      /free\n        FailureNo = 1;\n        SetLl Key_GPS HSGPSLF3;\n        ReadE Key_GPS HSGPSLF3;\n        DoW Not %Eof(HSGPSLF3);\n           If GPS150 > failureNo;\n              createFail(failureNo:groups:partNo:maintenance:text:\n                         valueMat:valueLab:valueSpe);\n              FailureNo = GPS150;\n              Maintenance = *Off;\n              clear text;\n              lineNo = 0;\n              valueMat = 0;\n              valueLab = 0;\n              valueSpe = 0;\n              groups = *Blanks;\n              partNo = *Blanks;\n              partValue = 0;\n           EndIf;\n           If GPS150 > 0;\n              create = *On;\n              GPS020 = %Subst(%EditC(GPS150:'X'):2:2);\n              GPS025 = '00';\n              //Check if Maintenance Standard time\n              If GPS040 = 'MAT';\n                 Chain GPS050 ITLSMF3;\n                 If %Found(ITLSMF3) And SFRAN = 'SC';\n                    If GPS070 > partValue;\n                       partNo = GPS050;\n                       partValue = GPS070;\n                    EndIf;\n                 EndIf;\n              EndIf;\n              Exec SQL Set :GPS080U = Upper(:GPS080);\n              If GPS040 = 'ARB' And %Scan('WARTUNG':GPS080U) > 0;\n                 Maintenance = *On;\n                 groups = %Subst(GPS050:1:4);\n              EndIf;\n              //Retrieve Main and Subgroup\n              If GPS040 = 'ARB' And Groups = *Blanks;\n                 groups = %Subst(GPS050:1:4);\n              EndIf;\n              If GPS040 = 'TXT' And %Subst(GPS080:1:1) <> '+' and lineNo < 4;\n                 lineNo +=1;\n                 text(lineNo) = GPS080;\n              EndIf;\n              Select;\n              When GPS040 = 'ARB';\n                 valueLab += GPS060 * GPS070;\n              When GPS040 = 'MAT';\n                 valueMat += GPS060 * GPS070;\n              When GPS040 = 'TXT';\n              Other;\n                 valueSpe += GPS070;\n              EndSl;\n           EndIf;\n           ReadE Key_GPS HSGPSLF3;\n        EndDo;\n        If create;\n           createFail(failureNo:groups:partNo:maintenance:text:\n                      valueMat:valueLab:valueSpe);\n           Chain (G71000:G71050:G71060) HSG71LF2;\n           If %Found(HSG71LF2);\n              G71170 = 3;\n              Update HSG71LR2;\n           EndIf;\n           If PKZ = 'SNF';\n              //sendClaim(G71000:G71050:*Blanks:*Blanks);\n           EndIf;\n        EndIf;\n        Unlock HSG71PF;\n        Unlock HSG73PF;\n       Return;\n      /end-free\n     P                 E",
